# Optical Depth Calculation
## formula
- 랑리 회귀식 : \\(\ln { I } =\ln { { E }_{ 0 } } +\ln { { I }_{ 0 } }-{\tau }_{tot}m \\)
    - \\(I \\) : 직달 일사량
    - \\({I}_{0} \\) : 전천 일사량
    - \\({E}_{0} \\) : 지구 궤도 이심률
    - \\({\tau }_{tot} \\) : Total AOD
    - \\(m=\frac { 1 }{ \cos{{\theta}_{0}} } \\)
- Total AOD : \\({ \tau  }_{ tot }={ \tau  }_{ Rayleigh }+{ \tau  }_{ ozone }+{ \tau  }_{ { NO }_{ 2 } }+{ \tau  }_{ { SO }_{ 2 } }+{ \tau  }_{ aerosol } \\)
    -

formula

paragraphs.title: calc diatance - make dataset
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
def get_station_latlon(spdf, location):
    tu = uvloc.where('location = "%s"' % location).collect()
    tu = (tu[0]['lat'], tu[0]['lon'])
    return tu

def make_latlon_list(spdf):
    src = spdf.collect()
    dst = []
    for row in src:
        if row['lat'] != 0.0:
            dst.append((row['location'], (float(row['lat']), float(row['lon']))))
    
    return dst

# uvlist = make_latlon_list(uvloc)
pmlist = make_latlon_list(pmloc)
print(pmlist)

paragraphs.title: find nearest stations
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

def find_nearest_stations(target_uv_station, distance_limit):
    from haversine import haversine

    # target_uv_station = '안면도'
    # distance_limit = 30  # unit = km
    
    spdf = []
    print(':::: find the nearest pm measure station ::::')
    anmyeon = get_station_latlon(uvloc, target_uv_station)
    print('target uv station:',  target_uv_station, anmyeon)
    print('>> result:')
    for location, latlon in pmlist:
        # print(anmyeon, latlon, 'distance:', haversine(anmyeon, latlon))
        if haversine(anmyeon, latlon) < distance_limit:
            # search
            searched_row = pmloc.where('location = "%s"' % location).collect()[0]
            # print
            print(searched_row, ', distance = %.2f' % haversine(anmyeon, latlon), 'km')
            spdf.append(searched_row)
    
    return spark.createDataFrame(spdf)
